				<MudText Style="color: #333333; font-size: 20px; font-family: 'Noto Serif', serif; font-weight: 700;">93% of customers say that their buying decisions are influenced by online reviews. CRI will drive customers to your business using SureCritic to enhance your reputation and increase positive social sharing.</MudText>
