			<MudItem xs="5" Style=@($"background-color: {Colors.Grey.Lighten2}; padding-top: 30px;")>
				<MudText Style="color: #333333; font-size: 14px; font-style: italic; font-family: 'Noto Serif', serif; font-weight: 400;">“SureCritic is a great partner for us. The ratings and review space can make or break our reputation, so it is key that we have verified customer reviews show up in search results when a prospect searches on our business. We also use Social Engage and we are already seeing an increase in Google Places reviews, as well as social media interactions.”</MudText>
